<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="3">胡能有定이리오마 報我不述다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="3">엇디 能히 定홈이 이시리오마 나 報호 述티 아니다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="06b" n="4">日月 四章</sent>

